{"tid":1244690,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯5次攻破巴拉圭球門居生涯之最，其中4次十二碼破門","createTime":"2019-06-20T04:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T10:09:31.000Z","uid":30768,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"83ced3f90556c87b1c1d503cf705d53054e2af68","tid":1244690,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"在阿根廷1-1戰平巴拉圭的比賽中，美斯罰入十二碼扳平比分，打入個人國家隊生涯的68球。這是美斯第5次洞穿巴拉圭球門，而巴拉圭也不幸成為了被美斯進球次數最多的國家隊。<br />\n<br />\n巧合的是，這5粒進球全是通過定位球打進的，包括4粒十二碼和1粒罰球。美斯上一次攻破巴拉圭的球門是在四年前的美洲杯小組賽，當時兩隊同樣戰成平局。"},{"pid":"a223262a0ef9503f5d5b7253d1f5fb8d0f61f9b1","tid":1244690,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:41:39.000Z","msg":"屌買撚左上盤,一撚係就輸埋佢啦`<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e303a7f569b4205b1b05ac9119de66ae303b22","tid":1244690,"uid":5649,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:41:50.000Z","msg":"4粒十二碼和1粒罰球<br />\n靠隊友餵死球既上帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be8fdb7165cae7f634086258edfa5a71ff7d9ad","tid":1244690,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b2e303a7f569b4205b1b05ac9119de66ae303b22","tid":1244690,"uid":5649,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:41:50.000Z","msg":"4粒十二碼和1粒罰球<br />\n靠隊友餵死球既上帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:48:54.000Z","msg":"米反上帝啦"},{"pid":"1af142f544d418e2cd19c89ce193ded9827a0fb7","tid":1244690,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"花迷又要打j了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5979525ec4a8612ef9eaa5f80232e1ec9b3e9085","tid":1244690,"uid":23385,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"真十二碼球王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor